<h1>Help & FAQ</h1>

<h2>Installation</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Install the app from the Shopify App Store.</li>
  <li>Approve required permissions.</li>
  <li>Enable the Theme App Extension to activate the live chat widget.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Uninstallation</h2>
<p>Uninstall the app from your Shopify admin. Store data associated with the app will be deleted in accordance with our Privacy Policy.</p>

<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
<p>If the chat widget is not visible, ensure the Theme App Extension is enabled and published.</p>

<h2>Billing</h2>
<p>Subscription charges are handled through Shopify billing.</p>

<h2>Data Requests</h2>
<p>To request data access or deletion, contact privacy@gosqo.com.</p>

